Title: Idiots are People Three!
Plot: Tracy Jordan challenges Liz by leading his own protest in defense of idiots everywhere. Jack faces off with Devin Banks yet again, but still finds time to interfere with Liz's relationship by giving Criss an ultimatum, and Liz tries to get rid of Jenna's new assistant.
GuestStars: Kelsey Grammer, Denise Richards, Marceline Hugot, James Marsden, Will Arnett
